01:36.620 --> 01:40.980
=Love Trip=

01:41.820 --> 01:42.980
=Episode 5=

01:42.980 --> 01:46.080
(Han Residence)

01:46.080 --> 01:49.900
(Kediaman Han Li)

02:07.920 --> 02:08.960
The change in your appearance is quite good.

02:15.280 --> 02:15.800
See you later.

02:22.120 --> 02:24.030
Come on, don't cry.

02:24.840 --> 02:26.280
OK, don't cry anymore.

02:26.430 --> 02:27.400
Why does he keep crying?

02:27.560 --> 02:29.310
- Good boy, don't cry.
- Do not Cry anymore.

02:29.430 --> 02:31.990
Why do you think a new baby was born
in a few days ?

02:32.120 --> 02:34.840
Can you experience diarrhea,
fever and rashes?

02:34.960 --> 02:36.280
Could it be that he caught a cold

02:36.280 --> 02:37.710
because it was brought out
to meet the guests

02:37.840 --> 02:38.910
at the baby bathing banquet today?

02:39.030 --> 02:41.520
Guard, quickly call a doctor.

02:41.640 --> 02:43.400
- Don't cry, okay?
- Don't cry.

02:43.560 --> 02:45.750
- Ok, it is finished.
- Fine, I'll go right away.

02:45.910 --> 02:46.800
OK, don't cry anymore.

02:46.910 --> 02:48.870
Soon it will be fine.
The healer will be here soon.

02:49.470 --> 02:51.280
- I'm very anxious.
- Don't cry, okay?

02:55.910 --> 02:57.870
- Don't cry anymore, okay?
- Good boy.

02:57.960 --> 03:00.150
- That's it, don't cry anymore.
- Very worrying.

03:00.240 --> 03:00.960
The healer has arrived, madam.

03:01.150 --> 03:04.190
Healer, hurry up. Quickly check
what happened to him.

03:07.520 --> 03:07.960
This.

03:26.960 --> 03:28.960
(Han Li, Bawahan Sun Jingdan
Gubernur Bingzhou)

03:28.960 --> 03:30.310
A very brave criminal.

03:30.840 --> 03:31.960
How dare he sneak
into the residence

03:32.080 --> 03:33.840
when there are many guests
at the baby's bathing event

03:33.990 --> 03:35.360
and kidnapped my grandson!

03:36.190 --> 03:37.590
He also left messages
openly

03:37.750 --> 03:39.190
and asked me to exchange it
for Military Plates.

03:41.840 --> 03:43.240
Please calm down, Mr. Big.

03:44.030 --> 03:47.310
Be careful when dealing
with bad people.

03:48.680 --> 03:51.360
Chengzhi, menuutmu,

03:51.710 --> 03:55.120
who dares to
do this?

03:57.400 --> 03:59.520
(Lv Chengzhi, Advisor to Han Li)
The Western Border Army just now

03:59.520 --> 04:02.310
was defeated in Wangzhou City
and is not far from us.

04:03.190 --> 04:07.150
Young Master Cui of the Cui Family Team
also led the team around here.

04:07.840 --> 04:13.080
Now, both families
had their eyes set on Bingzhou.

04:14.560 --> 04:17.030
There is no need to worry about
the Western Border Army

04:17.350 --> 04:18.350
who lost his family.

04:19.960 --> 04:25.790
It's just that Young Master Cui is
quite troublesome.

04:26.910 --> 04:29.280
Currently, he had kidnapped
the Little Young Master

04:29.470 --> 04:32.400
and told us
to put on Military Plates

04:32.520 --> 04:33.960
in the forest outside the city.

04:34.440 --> 04:38.230
Otherwise, they will
hurt Little Young Master.

04:43.520 --> 04:47.440
Give them fake Military Plates .

04:48.840 --> 04:49.400
Good.

05:19.470 --> 05:21.470
Luckily you pretended
to be a pregnant woman

05:21.670 --> 05:22.760
when we moved here.

05:23.550 --> 05:26.590
Otherwise, the appearance of a
crying baby for no reason

05:26.910 --> 05:28.470
will definitely make people suspicious.

05:36.110 --> 05:36.670
Wait a minute.

05:40.470 --> 05:42.350
It should be fortunate
that you can't walk

05:42.470 --> 05:43.520
while on a mountain road,

05:43.910 --> 05:45.590
then I asked you
to pretend to be a pregnant woman.

05:46.080 --> 05:48.350
Do you think I
understand things very carefully?

05:49.640 --> 05:52.030
His Majesty the Imperial Grandson
is really good at disguising traces

05:52.200 --> 05:53.200
and also remove the shadow.

05:57.840 --> 05:59.230
Why is he crying again?

06:00.320 --> 06:02.910
Your Majesty the Imperial Grandson,
it's time to change the swaddling clothes again.

06:04.280 --> 06:05.150
Why me again?

06:05.320 --> 06:07.150
That's because you understand something
very carefully.

06:12.030 --> 06:13.790
I'm really scared of you.

06:15.520 --> 06:18.230
Come on, don't cry anymore. Here.

06:19.280 --> 06:20.640
Don't cry, okay?

06:21.440 --> 06:22.440
Why do you have so much poop?

06:27.110 --> 06:28.640
- Big boss!
- How?

06:28.840 --> 06:30.350
Grand Master,
I have ordered people

06:30.550 --> 06:33.760
to guard the forest closely,
but it was almost dark

06:33.910 --> 06:35.760
and no one came
to collect the Military Plates.

06:36.030 --> 06:38.030
- No one?
- Correct.

06:38.400 --> 06:41.230
I was afraid that Old Master would be worried
so went back first.

06:42.230 --> 06:46.880
Big Master, according to you, will they
hurt Little Young Master

06:47.000 --> 06:48.710
if you don't get Military Plates?

06:51.140 --> 06:53.620
(Han Residence)

07:08.960 --> 07:10.230
You have to grow well.

07:10.400 --> 07:11.790
That way,
the Emperor's Grandson was not wasted

07:11.960 --> 07:13.640
wash a lot of diapers for you.

07:17.520 --> 07:18.880
Come on, let's go light a fire.

07:19.030 --> 07:21.670
Later, you have to be careful.
Don't burn this room down.

07:22.400 --> 07:24.110
- I already know.
- Come on.

07:29.550 --> 07:34.910
- Fire!
- Fire!

07:35.710 --> 07:36.640
Fire?

07:37.150 --> 07:40.440
This is bad, the enemy probably already knows
that the Military Plate is fake

07:41.400 --> 07:42.760
and came to pick up
the original Military Plates.

07:43.030 --> 07:44.440
Quickly send someone to the south courtyard.

07:44.590 --> 07:46.110
Prepare more water
to prevent burns.

08:18.670 --> 08:20.840
Now, we know
the whereabouts of genuine Military Plates.

08:21.110 --> 08:24.280
However, there were so many arrows
and traps set in the yard.

08:24.680 --> 08:25.660
We cannot break through by force.

08:26.670 --> 08:27.960
Let's go back first
to think about how.

08:28.640 --> 08:29.520
- Come on.
- Come on.

08:32.830 --> 08:34.070
Big boss.

08:34.830 --> 08:36.670
Unexpectedly, someone
deliberately started the fire.

08:36.790 --> 08:37.600
Even more unexpected,

08:37.760 --> 08:40.000
someone returned
the Little Young Master to his room.

08:42.280 --> 08:44.120
Luckily
the fire was extinguished.

08:44.830 --> 08:47.950
Little Young Master is safe and fine.

08:48.430 --> 08:50.190
This is a two-pronged strategy

08:50.400 --> 08:51.920
deliberately made me go
to see the Military Plates.

08:53.600 --> 08:55.310
They took advantage of the fire situation

08:55.550 --> 08:57.760
to make everyone in the residence
panic and steal the Military Plates.

09:00.720 --> 09:05.030
It would be good if they really
came to steal the Military Plates.

09:05.520 --> 09:08.240
The security of the southern courtyard where
the Military Plate was located was very tight.

09:08.480 --> 09:12.550
Without 1,800 people,
no one could break through.

09:23.190 --> 09:24.880
We already know
the existence of Military Plates,

09:25.000 --> 09:27.640
but supervision is very strict.

09:28.280 --> 09:29.830
Looks like it would be difficult to steal it.

09:31.310 --> 09:33.240
Since you can't steal
secretly,

09:34.950 --> 09:36.600
we try to outwit them.

09:42.150 --> 09:44.190
How about we pretend to be
envoys from the Western Border Army

09:44.520 --> 09:47.360
and went to face Han Li?

09:47.910 --> 09:48.600
Can't.

09:49.760 --> 09:52.790
The Western Border Army had just
returned from losing at Wangzhou City.

09:53.070 --> 09:55.190
Han Li will definitely not
be kind to us.

10:05.030 --> 10:08.720
We'd better pretend
to be the Cui Family Team's emissaries.

10:09.150 --> 10:12.880
We go to talk to Han Li
that we want to borrow the Jianzhou road

10:13.190 --> 10:14.190
and promises profit for him.

10:14.600 --> 10:15.790
Han Li is a greedy person.

10:16.240 --> 10:18.030
Your Cui Family Army
has a very high reputation.

10:18.280 --> 10:19.280
Most likely he will agree.

10:20.430 --> 10:22.720
Grandson of the Emperor,
you are truly sincere and honest.

10:23.120 --> 10:24.120
We can get Military Plates,

10:24.120 --> 10:25.240
as long as Han Li sends people
to Jianzhou

10:25.240 --> 10:26.190
to take Military Plates,

10:26.480 --> 10:28.360
at that time we can rob him
and kill him in the middle of the road

10:28.600 --> 10:29.830
or exchange the fake
for the original.

10:30.030 --> 10:31.520
If you succeed in getting a Military Plate,

10:31.600 --> 10:32.870
Western Border Army
and Cui Family Army

10:33.000 --> 10:34.120
each took one city.

10:34.480 --> 10:35.640
Always Bingzhou.

10:37.550 --> 10:38.790
We better make a deal.

10:40.600 --> 10:43.430
Whichever of us captures
or kills Han Li first,

10:44.030 --> 10:45.070
he is the one who will get Bingzhou.

10:45.880 --> 10:47.400
Whichever of us gets
the Military Plate first,

10:47.720 --> 10:48.910
he was the one who got Jianzhou.

10:51.790 --> 10:55.360
What if I capture Han Li
and also obtain a Military Plate?

10:55.480 --> 10:56.640
Bingzhou, Jianzhou,
everything is yours.

10:56.880 --> 10:58.640
The Western Border Army
will not say anything,

10:59.000 --> 10:59.950
vice versa.

11:00.190 --> 11:00.880
Good.

11:01.120 --> 11:03.910
If Jianzhou and Bingzhou
belonged to the Western Border Army,

11:04.070 --> 11:06.720
Jianzhou has always been an important route
to the east and north.

11:06.830 --> 11:07.960
Later,
Cui Family Army military merchants

11:08.030 --> 11:09.430
will use the road
to cross the border,

11:09.550 --> 11:11.360
The Western Border Force
cannot refuse.

11:11.830 --> 11:12.880
And vice versa.

11:14.280 --> 11:15.310
Clap my hands as a sign of agreement.

11:18.600 --> 11:20.720
Sir,
Chen Xing sent a reply.

11:20.950 --> 11:22.910
Finally, the mark left
by Commander He was discovered

11:23.280 --> 11:24.830
in a very hidden place
in Bingzhou City.

11:25.310 --> 11:27.000
Good, very good.

11:27.600 --> 11:30.910
Taozi, you go to Bingzhou City
to see Chen Xing,

11:31.360 --> 11:32.360
and help the Commander.

11:33.670 --> 11:38.030
Bingzhou was Han Li's territory.
People are easily suspicious.

11:38.670 --> 11:41.280
If you come bringing
a group of soldiers slowly,

11:41.790 --> 11:43.240
I'm afraid
he will harm the Commander.

11:44.480 --> 11:45.150
Lin.

11:45.150 --> 11:46.520
(Cui Li, General of the Cui Family Army)

11:51.600 --> 11:53.600
Brother, why did you come?

11:55.120 --> 11:57.670
Lin, you fought outside
for several months.

11:58.000 --> 11:59.950
As an older brother, how could
I not worry about you?

12:00.400 --> 12:00.830
Now,

12:01.190 --> 12:03.240
Uncle sent me to the western mountains
to take care of something.

12:04.000 --> 12:06.520
I also think that the western mountain
is very close to your place

12:06.880 --> 12:09.830
so I immediately brought my entourage
to come to meet you.

12:10.480 --> 12:12.430
As brothers, we work together
to kill the enemy

12:12.760 --> 12:16.030
so that Uncle knows that this is his nephew

12:16.400 --> 12:17.880
can also achieve
brilliant achievements.

12:19.240 --> 12:23.000
Brother, your actions
violate military orders.

12:27.280 --> 12:28.280
Lin, just calm down.

12:28.830 --> 12:30.070
I've sent someone
to report it

12:30.120 --> 12:30.910
to Uncle as soon as possible.

12:31.070 --> 12:32.910
I'm sure
Uncle will definitely agree.

12:33.190 --> 12:36.520
Besides, just think about it,
if my thousands of troops returned alone,

12:36.670 --> 12:39.070
What if something happens
while traveling?

12:43.430 --> 12:45.070
Since you have already reported it
to my father,

12:45.720 --> 12:47.550
set up camp and rest.

12:52.400 --> 12:54.400
The soldiers are still here.

12:55.430 --> 12:56.830
What is your plan?

12:57.480 --> 13:00.070
Brother, since you came here
in violation of military orders,

13:00.430 --> 13:02.400
you have to hold back your troops

13:02.760 --> 13:04.600
and may not discuss
any military matters.

13:06.310 --> 13:09.120
Otherwise, when you go back
to my father's place,

13:09.310 --> 13:11.150
accept the punishment for the offense
you committed.

13:16.240 --> 13:20.480
How dare that sick person
speak rudely to me.

13:21.190 --> 13:24.760
This Cui Lin just happened
to be reincarnated with good fortune.

13:25.150 --> 13:26.720
If I were Uncle's son,

13:27.280 --> 13:29.760
The entire Cui Family Army
has long been under my command.

13:30.720 --> 13:32.240
Third Lord, don't be emotional.

13:32.400 --> 13:34.000
Cui Lin has been sickly and weak
since childhood.

13:34.070 --> 13:37.150
He took medication for years.
It probably won't last long.

13:37.480 --> 13:39.600
At that time,
the Great General had no sons,

13:39.760 --> 13:42.150
won't the Cui Family Team
be yours?

13:48.430 --> 13:50.430
I humbled myself
for years.

13:51.480 --> 13:53.190
With the current
turbulent situation,

13:55.000 --> 13:56.640
I really can't
wait any longer.

13:59.150 --> 14:01.360
Does Third Master want to...

14:04.240 --> 14:06.550
The reason I humbled myself
to follow Cui Lin

14:07.190 --> 14:09.000
is to act according to the situation.

14:09.600 --> 14:12.310
With one action,
I will get rid of

14:13.520 --> 14:15.190
Cui Lin and also Commander He.

14:23.670 --> 14:27.430
The two of you came here
under Young Master Cui's orders

14:27.790 --> 14:31.000
to borrow the Jianzhou road
for the Cui Family Army?

14:31.910 --> 14:35.280
That's right, we hope
Mr. Han agrees.

14:37.640 --> 14:40.000
This is easy to talk about.

14:41.120 --> 14:43.760
However, Military Commander Sun in the capital

14:44.030 --> 14:46.000
always ordered me strictly
to defend the city.

14:46.670 --> 14:48.670
If I agree to lend it,

14:49.240 --> 14:53.000
it's possible that Commander Sun will
punish me.

14:53.480 --> 14:55.070
Since we came to borrow
from Mr. Han,

14:55.550 --> 14:58.760
The Cui family had naturally
prepared reciprocity.

15:00.830 --> 15:02.950
Gathering merchants from both cities,

15:03.670 --> 15:06.360
went to Pingliang City and Weiyang
where the Cui Family was located

15:06.480 --> 15:07.430
to sell silk.

15:08.150 --> 15:09.760
As long as Mr. Han
agrees to lend it,

15:10.240 --> 15:11.000
then later,

15:11.360 --> 15:13.030
we will not levy silk tax
on traders

15:13.150 --> 15:14.360
located in both cities.

15:15.000 --> 15:20.400
I think Mr. Han definitely understands
the tax benefits.

15:23.430 --> 15:28.520
You two came from a long way
and it's already late today.

15:28.830 --> 15:33.120
How about you rest
at my residence while drinking wine?

15:33.400 --> 15:35.120
The team you lead
is near here.

15:35.600 --> 15:36.640
We couldn't stay any longer.

15:36.910 --> 15:39.120
We have to go back as soon as possible
to report to Master.

15:47.720 --> 15:51.150
Good. You two, please sit down.

15:52.910 --> 15:55.360
Wait for me to discuss this first.

16:05.040 --> 16:08.360
(Kota Wangzhou)

16:25.760 --> 16:26.640
What are you doing?

16:27.550 --> 16:29.950
Second Brother,
why your Western Border Army

16:30.070 --> 16:31.400
fighting this strangely?

16:31.600 --> 16:32.720
Night is coming,

16:32.910 --> 16:35.070
we are all outside Wangzhou City
to feed mosquitoes.

16:35.880 --> 16:37.120
Brother Chang'er already said,

16:37.120 --> 16:38.830
He didn't let us come,
but you insisted on coming.

16:39.950 --> 16:41.880
Since it has come, we should
obey Brother Chang'er's words.

16:44.640 --> 16:46.000
However, what
are we actually doing here?

16:52.070 --> 16:54.120
You said one of the messengers

16:54.120 --> 16:56.240
is Commander He
of the Cui Family Army?

16:59.240 --> 17:02.360
That meant she was
Young Master Cui's advisor girl

17:02.360 --> 17:04.790
the famous surname He?

17:06.590 --> 17:08.110
I know food traders

17:08.440 --> 17:10.160
who had long been connected
with the Cui Family Army.

17:10.630 --> 17:12.760
Just now, when I heard
that the Cui Family Army

17:12.870 --> 17:14.030
sent a messenger here,

17:14.480 --> 17:16.070
I ordered him
to check secretly.

17:16.350 --> 17:17.240
It's confirmed

17:20.110 --> 17:21.720
that she was indeed the counselor's girl.

17:22.630 --> 17:23.760
No wonder.

17:24.630 --> 17:25.960
I'm thinking too

17:26.070 --> 17:28.630
why is it one of the two envoys
from the Cui Family Army

17:28.760 --> 17:32.070
is a girl in disguise.

17:33.240 --> 17:38.440
Turns out, she was
the famous counselor girl surnamed He.

17:40.160 --> 17:41.720
I heard too

17:41.790 --> 17:45.480
that the girl surnamed He
was Young Master Cui's confidant

17:45.550 --> 17:48.070
and often gave him advice.

17:49.310 --> 17:53.790
The other messenger
had extraordinary tolerance.

17:54.590 --> 17:57.870
At his current age, having
such extraordinary tolerance

18:00.280 --> 18:02.960
also makes me suspicious.

18:14.680 --> 18:16.240
Why is Mr. Han
paying this kind of respect?

18:17.790 --> 18:23.870
Young Master Cui came in such a disguise
that it frightened me.

18:31.920 --> 18:34.310
Since Master Han
has revealed Young Master's identity,

18:34.760 --> 18:37.680
we face each other honestly.

18:39.520 --> 18:41.280
Master Han took over
and built two cities.

18:41.920 --> 18:43.350
Master really has
a broad outlook.

18:44.350 --> 18:47.160
This time, Young Master Cui came
in person.

18:47.280 --> 18:50.590
In any case, the matter of borrowing the road
can definitely be discussed.

18:50.720 --> 18:51.680
Can be discussed.

18:52.160 --> 18:54.480
Then,
thank you very much, Mr. Han.

18:55.350 --> 18:56.030
Waiter.

18:57.590 --> 18:59.280
- I am here.
- Quickly prepare the banquet.

18:59.760 --> 19:02.480
I will drink wine
with Young Master Cui.

19:11.520 --> 19:13.790
Good, the first time fighting
was really fun.

19:13.960 --> 19:14.070
Correct.

19:14.200 --> 19:15.030
Much more exciting than robbing
and giving to the poor.

19:15.200 --> 19:16.630
- Correct.
- Correct.

19:16.760 --> 19:18.920
Being a bandit is not as exciting
as being a soldier.

19:19.030 --> 19:20.000
So true.

19:24.280 --> 19:25.390
(Western Frontier)
Western Frontier!

19:26.480 --> 19:30.390
Western Frontier! I'm back!

19:35.030 --> 19:35.960
Friends!

19:37.680 --> 19:41.280
Friends, come with me
and take back Wangzhou!

19:41.480 --> 19:46.920
(Li)
Take back Wangzhou!

20:17.550 --> 20:21.630
Young Master Cui,
how about this dance?

20:23.680 --> 20:27.070
I left my hometown
and fought in the war,

20:27.350 --> 20:28.440
Haven't seen a dance in a long time.

20:29.070 --> 20:32.480
The current scene deserves to be called
peace, luxury, and honor.

20:34.160 --> 20:35.870
Muda Muda praises too much.

20:36.350 --> 20:41.960
Young Master Cui is humble,
I feel very moved.

21:02.200 --> 21:04.240
Young Master Cui, please enjoy it.

21:05.070 --> 21:11.350
There was a small problem in the back hall,
I left for a while and came back soon.

21:12.680 --> 21:13.440
Go ahead, Mr. Han.

21:27.590 --> 21:30.830
Military Commander Sun sent a messenger

21:30.830 --> 21:33.110
and give a
very valuable property.

21:33.240 --> 21:35.790
I feel a little scared.

21:35.790 --> 21:37.140
(Leader Messenger Sun Jing)
The Military Commander said,

21:37.440 --> 21:38.730
it is very difficult for Mr. Han
to take responsibility

21:38.790 --> 21:41.870
over the two cities and confront the rebels
on the Western Border directly.

21:42.030 --> 21:44.760
So, I was specially ordered
to send all of these from the capital.

21:45.200 --> 21:47.790
They are all rare treasures
carefully selected

21:47.870 --> 21:51.110
by the Military Commander from his own funds
as a tribute to Tuan Han.

21:52.110 --> 21:53.550
Many thanks
to the Military Commander.

21:53.720 --> 21:57.110
I received the reward for free,
I really have to be grateful for it.

21:57.680 --> 21:59.030
Mr. Han is too humble.

22:00.680 --> 22:02.000
I want to know

22:02.110 --> 22:05.030
Is there a message or order
from the Military Commander?

22:05.160 --> 22:07.630
If that's the case, of course there is.

22:08.030 --> 22:10.030
Actually, the Military Commander
sent me here,

22:10.160 --> 22:13.160
firstly because he knows
that I have known Mr. Han for a long time,

22:13.630 --> 22:15.760
This trip is perfect
for us to chat.

22:15.960 --> 22:18.720
Second, the Military Commander is also worried

22:18.870 --> 22:23.760
with cruel arrows on the battlefield
and safety of Lord Han.

22:25.070 --> 22:26.280
So, I was specially ordered

22:26.280 --> 22:28.630
to bring
these 12 golden armored guards.

22:30.790 --> 22:32.030
I ordered the guards

22:32.280 --> 22:35.070
to stay
by Tuan Han's side all day.

22:35.440 --> 22:39.550
They must protect
Master Han completely.

22:41.870 --> 22:46.440
The Military Commander
is very caring and kind.

22:46.760 --> 22:50.160
I am so grateful
and cannot repay you enough.

22:50.480 --> 22:52.720
Just by personally leading the guard troops

22:52.830 --> 22:54.390
to fight against
the Western Border Army

22:54.520 --> 22:56.000
and other traitors,

22:56.160 --> 22:58.760
I can only repay
the kindness of the Military Commander.

23:03.070 --> 23:05.390
The Military Commander's move this time
was to force Mr. Big

23:05.520 --> 23:06.830
to be hostile
to the two families.

23:07.760 --> 23:12.280
Otherwise, he couldn't have sent
12 golden-armored guards here.

23:12.870 --> 23:14.280
They said
to protect Mr. Big,

23:14.630 --> 23:17.790
but actually wants to suppress Master Han.

23:22.200 --> 23:24.720
Sun Jing declared himself
Military Commander

23:25.280 --> 23:27.160
and destroyed the entire Li Family.

23:28.000 --> 23:30.830
He also gave
me something called a covenant.

23:32.590 --> 23:36.390
At that time, I just responded
carelessly.

23:37.000 --> 23:40.310
Unexpectedly even
exceeding the limit and going further.

23:40.550 --> 23:43.790
Big Master, the Cui Family members
are still in the banquet hall.

23:44.680 --> 23:49.830
This matter must not be known
by the Leader Envoy from Sun Jing.

23:51.310 --> 23:56.110
We can use the Cui Family members .

23:57.790 --> 24:00.200
Cui Yi only had one son.

24:01.830 --> 24:05.280
Unexpectedly,
he even came to my place himself.

24:06.390 --> 24:09.760
Then, don't blame me
if I'm rude.

24:32.520 --> 24:34.440
Young Master, you are drunk.

24:34.960 --> 24:36.070
I'm not drunk.

24:38.960 --> 24:39.720
Something is wrong.

24:42.790 --> 24:45.390
Young Master, I'll take you back
to rest.

24:51.680 --> 24:52.590
Young Master Cui is drunk.

24:52.960 --> 24:54.520
Papa Young Master
to rest in the guest room!

25:11.350 --> 25:12.160
Young Master, wait a minute!

25:14.680 --> 25:18.520
Young Master Cui,
since you guys have come,

25:19.160 --> 25:21.200
why rush to leave like that?

25:21.830 --> 25:25.070
The way you treat guests
is too excessive, right?

25:27.110 --> 25:28.920
If you don't hold the young master today,

25:29.240 --> 25:30.520
I couldn't
finish my assignment either.

25:31.000 --> 25:32.790
I was forced to kill
this girl surnamed He

25:33.110 --> 25:34.680
to explain it to the Master.

25:39.830 --> 25:43.520
Good. I can stay here,
but you have to let go.

25:47.000 --> 25:48.280
Young Master take it easy.

25:48.870 --> 25:51.960
If a distinguished guest
like Young Master lives in Bingzhou,

25:52.310 --> 25:55.520
the entire Cui Family Army
would have no worries.

25:56.160 --> 25:57.310
Of course, I have to let it be

25:57.310 --> 26:00.920
Miss He went back
and explained it to General Cui

26:01.310 --> 26:03.000
to avoid misunderstanding.

26:05.030 --> 26:05.870
Young Master, go quickly.

26:06.520 --> 26:08.110
Don't pay attention to these untrustworthy villains .

26:22.310 --> 26:25.960
Good! Young Master Cui
is very loving and loyal,

26:26.110 --> 26:27.550
also appreciate beautiful women.

26:38.440 --> 26:39.680
Young Master take it easy.

26:40.960 --> 26:42.520
Doors, windows and roof here

26:42.870 --> 26:45.680
everything is coated with fine steel
so it is very safe.

26:45.870 --> 26:49.000
No killer will
be able to come.

26:50.110 --> 26:50.870
Prison is still prison,

26:51.000 --> 26:52.390
why say it
that well?

26:55.720 --> 26:56.350
Why?

26:56.790 --> 27:00.870
How can this beautiful place
not be a good place?

27:03.760 --> 27:04.310
Wait a minute.

27:05.630 --> 27:06.760
Prepare hot water here.

27:07.200 --> 27:09.310
Muda Muda really likes cleanliness.

27:09.590 --> 27:11.390
I want to serve him a bath.

27:17.630 --> 27:20.870
Good. I will order people
to prepare scented water.

27:21.030 --> 27:22.310
Also prepare a thick cloth

27:22.480 --> 27:25.310
to prevent Young Master
from catching cold when bathing.

27:25.480 --> 27:28.160
If our Young Master feels
the slightest discomfort

27:28.200 --> 27:29.280
while in Bingzhou City,

27:29.480 --> 27:32.920
The Cui Family's forces
will definitely flatten Bingzhou.

27:37.390 --> 27:40.310
I'll get
a thick cloth for you.

28:55.440 --> 28:58.030
- Young Master, you can take a shower.
- Good.

29:26.960 --> 29:27.720
There are people on the roof.

29:29.030 --> 29:29.630
How about this?

29:43.960 --> 29:46.070
The water temperature is right,
how about we shower together?

30:40.760 --> 30:41.180
Wait a minute.

30:49.440 --> 30:51.480
Already. You can
talk now.

30:54.790 --> 30:55.520
What are you laughing at?

30:56.480 --> 30:59.630
I laughed at
our first meeting

31:00.350 --> 31:01.960
it seems similar to now.

31:02.680 --> 31:05.680
Yes Don't you know
that at that time you were so fierce?

31:05.870 --> 31:06.960
As soon as you come,
you invite a fight.

31:07.160 --> 31:10.240
Nonsense.
Obviously you were the one who attacked first.

31:10.440 --> 31:13.160
Nonsense. Why would I attack you
if you don't take my pearls?

31:13.520 --> 31:14.440
What pearl?

31:16.480 --> 31:19.160
That broken belt?
I've thrown it away.

31:20.070 --> 31:20.590
You...

31:23.680 --> 31:24.240
Why?

31:26.000 --> 31:31.590
Does the Emperor's Grandson also want to attack me now
?

31:39.310 --> 31:40.280
Let's talk seriously.

31:41.350 --> 31:42.720
What plans do you have?

31:44.110 --> 31:45.960
What plan?

31:46.480 --> 31:50.680
Of course I have to find a way
to return to the Cui Family Army,

31:50.830 --> 31:52.830
then come back
to save you, Young Master.

31:54.110 --> 31:55.280
Is it true?

31:56.070 --> 32:00.030
After returning to the Cui Family Army,
will you come back to save me?

32:03.550 --> 32:04.960
What are you doing?
What do you see?

32:10.630 --> 32:14.000
This Emperor's Grandson's head
was priceless.

32:14.790 --> 32:17.240
How could I be willing
not to come back to save you?

32:18.870 --> 32:20.240
You're really good at talking.

32:21.310 --> 32:23.200
I really like.

32:24.480 --> 32:25.760
Very like.

32:36.440 --> 32:40.070
I didn't think Young Master Cui
was such a loving person.

32:40.240 --> 32:42.160
- Yes.
- Just take a shower

32:42.590 --> 32:44.760
can bring out such charm.

32:45.440 --> 32:47.390
I've sent people
to watch over there.

32:47.870 --> 32:50.680
It's just that Miss He
is indeed a smart person.

32:50.870 --> 32:53.030
He not only covered
the doors and windows with thick cloth,

32:53.440 --> 32:55.200
but also cover
the copper pipes in the floor

32:55.310 --> 32:57.200
used for eavesdropping.

32:57.680 --> 32:59.070
I'm worried about our guards

32:59.520 --> 33:01.310
won't be able
to hear anything useful.

33:01.480 --> 33:02.480
No problem.

33:03.550 --> 33:08.030
Unexpectedly,
Young Master Cui was so relaxed

33:08.160 --> 33:09.680
- and harmonious with their partner.
- Correct.

33:09.830 --> 33:12.520
This shows
that he is indeed not an ordinary person.

33:13.520 --> 33:15.550
Although Cui Yi
only had one son,

33:16.280 --> 33:17.630
he is worth like ten sons.

33:19.200 --> 33:21.550
Very interesting.

33:40.030 --> 33:41.350
What are you doing?

33:42.760 --> 33:43.830
I want to ask you.

33:45.350 --> 33:46.310
Asking what?

33:46.830 --> 33:48.440
You still haven't told
me your name.

33:50.550 --> 33:52.110
Don't you know that my surname is He?

33:55.790 --> 33:58.280
What does your family's Young Master
usually call you?

33:59.920 --> 34:01.280
Why are you asking that question?

34:02.030 --> 34:04.550
Of course, I was afraid of being discovered
when in Han Li's presence.

34:04.790 --> 34:06.590
I couldn't possibly
call you a girl surnamed He, right?

34:07.920 --> 34:09.950
If you don't want to tell me,
I'll just pick a name for you.

34:12.990 --> 34:15.240
What good name can
you give me?

34:15.600 --> 34:18.040
Based on your behavior,
you will definitely give me

34:18.160 --> 34:20.160
bad names like Mao or Gou.
[*Means cat or dog]

34:24.120 --> 34:26.790
If I pay attention,
you look like Mao.

34:31.200 --> 34:32.350
You just call me Jin.

34:33.910 --> 34:35.720
Tried to fool me again
with a fake name.

34:36.640 --> 34:37.600
I don't want to.

34:39.390 --> 34:42.510
I'd better choose
a name for you, your name is Dao

34:43.390 --> 34:44.390
or Zhen can too.

34:51.990 --> 34:54.350
Why Dao or Zhen?

34:54.760 --> 34:55.640
Just guess for yourself.

34:57.830 --> 34:58.280
Dao?

34:59.600 --> 35:00.310
Zhen?

35:05.200 --> 35:06.280
You're laughing at me, aren't you?

35:06.470 --> 35:08.120
I pretended
to be a pregnant woman twice,

35:08.280 --> 35:09.720
once my stomach was filled with straw,
[*Dao means straw]

35:09.820 --> 35:11.040
another filled with pillows.
[*Zhen means pillow]

35:11.040 --> 35:12.200
How dare I.

35:12.640 --> 35:15.160
You really understand all my origins.

35:15.430 --> 35:17.830
I just asked your name,
you didn't want to tell me.

35:18.240 --> 35:19.870
I'm afraid Han Li
will become murderous.

35:20.600 --> 35:23.510
If I were killed,
I wouldn't even know your name.

35:24.390 --> 35:25.600
Isn't that a pity?

35:31.560 --> 35:32.600
Very fierce.

35:39.080 --> 35:39.990
My name is Ying.

35:43.240 --> 35:45.040
It was a nickname
given to me by my mother.

35:47.950 --> 35:49.430
(Ying?)

35:53.600 --> 35:54.350
Ying.

35:59.990 --> 36:01.240
Really good name.

36:33.350 --> 36:35.680
- Take a look over there.
- Check it out.

36:37.040 --> 36:37.600
Tie it tightly.

36:38.040 --> 36:39.390
- It's still here.
- Come on.

36:39.390 --> 36:44.830
(Wangzhou)

36:44.830 --> 36:46.390
Sister, look!

36:46.870 --> 36:47.830
Collect your weapons.

36:48.160 --> 36:48.790
Friends,

36:48.870 --> 36:50.950
- There are new weapons.
- How? You guys aren't hurt, right?

36:51.080 --> 36:52.470
- Nothing.
- Give it to him.

36:55.510 --> 36:57.950
Young General Pei,
there is something I don't understand.

36:58.120 --> 36:59.200
Can I ask you a question?

36:59.350 --> 37:00.760
Needless to say, let's say.

37:02.040 --> 37:03.280
I'm confused,

37:03.430 --> 37:05.040
why did the Western Border Army
leave Wangzhou?

37:05.200 --> 37:06.640
Then, I was also confused,

37:06.760 --> 37:08.040
why do we all
follow Young General Pei

37:08.160 --> 37:09.760
back to Wangzhou?

37:11.470 --> 37:14.430
I have discussed this
with Shiqi.

37:14.760 --> 37:18.510
If the enemy is too strong,
we cannot defend Wangzhou.

37:18.830 --> 37:19.990
The only way
is to pretend to retreat,

37:20.160 --> 37:22.240
then set up a hidden pillar
in Wangzhou City,

37:22.390 --> 37:25.310
poisoning soldiers' food
and drinking water,

37:25.310 --> 37:26.350
then spread the news

37:26.560 --> 37:28.680
to shake the soldiers' morale
and undermine its foundations.

37:28.720 --> 37:30.430
Lastly, we will work together
inside and out

37:30.560 --> 37:31.790
to retake Wangzhou.

37:32.990 --> 37:34.280
So it turns out.

37:34.950 --> 37:36.350
Of course, soldiers never tire
of trickery.

37:36.350 --> 37:36.990
Makes sense.

37:36.990 --> 37:37.990
Isn't that right, Chang'er?

37:38.760 --> 37:39.830
Come on, let's go into town.

37:40.040 --> 37:40.680
- Good!
- Come on!

37:40.680 --> 37:42.040
(Wangzhou)
Ayo.

38:10.200 --> 38:13.390
Concubine, there is still no news
from General Yun Chang.

38:13.720 --> 38:16.350
Who knows how things are going with him
and the Emperor's First Grandson.

38:18.470 --> 38:22.310
No news
is the best news.

38:22.580 --> 38:24.040
Come on, let's go see Jiang.

38:27.840 --> 38:30.080
(Jiang, Concubine of the Former Crown Prince)

38:33.430 --> 38:34.350
Crown Princess.

38:36.240 --> 38:37.470
This is not the past,

38:37.830 --> 38:39.790
So don't call me
that again.

38:40.950 --> 38:42.830
Yes, Concubine Xiao.

38:47.390 --> 38:50.600
How is your body condition
these few days?

38:52.080 --> 38:53.870
I feel fine.

38:53.870 --> 38:56.910
It's just that
I worry all day.

38:57.470 --> 38:58.720
Don't worry.

38:59.470 --> 39:03.600
Today, I come to tell you
that I have found the way.

39:03.990 --> 39:05.640
However, you have to wait a few days

39:06.240 --> 39:08.040
only then can I get you out
of the palace quietly.

39:09.470 --> 39:12.080
I will never forget Concubine's kindness.

39:12.240 --> 39:13.280
Quickly stand up.

39:15.560 --> 39:18.640
The baby you are carrying
is a descendant of the Crown Prince.

39:19.120 --> 39:21.430
Of course I have to find a way
to keep you safe.

39:22.910 --> 39:25.040
Concubine, we cannot
linger here.

39:27.600 --> 39:28.470
I go first.

39:29.040 --> 39:31.830
If there's any trouble, you know how
to find Aunt Shen.

39:32.600 --> 39:33.350
Can.

39:45.760 --> 39:46.680
- Young Master.
- Young Master.

39:46.790 --> 39:47.600
Taozi is back.

39:50.240 --> 39:50.720
Young Master.

39:51.080 --> 39:52.120
Is there any news about the Commander?

39:52.310 --> 39:53.920
There is. Chen Xing and I found out

39:53.920 --> 39:55.100
the latest mark left
by the Commander.

39:55.100 --> 39:55.830
He entered the Han Li Residence.

39:55.990 --> 39:56.720
Kediaman Han Li?

39:57.680 --> 39:59.390
The commander definitely had a plan
when he entered Han Li's Residence.

39:59.600 --> 40:02.350
I also tried to sneak inside,
but it was heavily guarded.

40:02.560 --> 40:04.120
I was afraid that the enemy would become alert
so came out first.

40:04.470 --> 40:05.470
I'm back to report

40:05.640 --> 40:07.640
Chen Xing stayed in Bingzhou City,
waiting to pick up the Commander.

40:07.990 --> 40:09.160
Apart from that, the secret report said

40:09.160 --> 40:10.940
that the leader's envoy sent
by Sun Jing also arrived in Bingzhou.

40:11.330 --> 40:13.120
Reportedly, he came there
bearing gifts for Han Li.

40:13.280 --> 40:15.990
He carried two large chests of goods,
as well as 12 gold-armored guards.

40:17.640 --> 40:19.430
Han Li, the cunning villain,

40:19.720 --> 40:23.280
always try to play both sides
without offending anyone.

40:24.860 --> 40:25.400
(Which)

40:25.990 --> 40:28.480
Taozi, take the flag of this letter
and go to the city in disguise.

40:28.680 --> 40:30.520
Give the letter flag
to Chen Xing

40:30.520 --> 40:32.950
and asked him to meet Han Li properly

40:33.120 --> 40:34.350
in the name of Cui Family Team Leader Envoy
.

40:34.680 --> 40:36.680
Remember to act
according to the situation.

40:37.240 --> 40:40.720
It would be even better if you could take advantage of
the messenger sent by Sun Jing.

40:41.120 --> 40:45.600
If Han Li dares to detain someone,
we must ask him,

40:45.600 --> 40:48.430
to see if
our team agrees or not.

41:06.680 --> 41:08.470
These are flowers
that were just picked today.

41:08.760 --> 41:10.760
The Old Master said that the Young Master
was a graceful person.

41:10.910 --> 41:12.430
Can't ignore

41:12.600 --> 41:14.160
food, clothing,
and daily life Tuan Muda.

41:14.430 --> 41:15.560
He specifically asked me

41:15.720 --> 41:18.240
sent these flowers
for Young Master to enjoy.

41:18.790 --> 41:20.910
Thank you very much.
You guys are really considerate.

41:21.680 --> 41:24.080
However, why
didn't your Great Master keep his promise?

41:24.950 --> 41:27.390
At that time, he clearly said
that if I surrendered,

41:28.160 --> 41:28.990
he will let it go.

41:29.870 --> 41:31.120
Why not keep the promise?

41:33.470 --> 41:36.350
Young Master, if you say that,
you blame our Grand Master.

41:36.990 --> 41:38.160
Our Grand Master has promised.

41:38.430 --> 41:39.640
Young Master, you are very honorable.

41:39.790 --> 41:44.560
Meanwhile, all our waiters
are rude and careless workers.

41:44.720 --> 41:46.200
We are afraid to ignore the Young Master.

41:48.310 --> 41:51.920
This Miss He is a person
who is considerate towards Young Master.

41:52.310 --> 41:53.680
If you live here,

41:54.350 --> 41:57.830
he could of course serve
the Young Master well.

41:59.280 --> 42:00.390
You're really good at talking.

42:01.390 --> 42:06.310
Please enjoy, Young Master.
I won't bother you anymore.

42:28.760 --> 42:29.240
Do not move.

42:33.680 --> 42:34.760
You're very relaxed, aren't you?

42:35.430 --> 42:38.160
After all, I'm stuck here
and have nothing to do.

42:38.790 --> 42:40.040
How about playing with me?

42:41.280 --> 42:41.790
Good.

42:42.510 --> 42:44.160
In that case, it would be more fun
if there were prizes.

42:44.430 --> 42:45.350
A gift?

42:46.640 --> 42:47.350
Let's make it like this.

42:48.160 --> 42:50.790
If I win,
you give me a hairpin on your head

42:51.120 --> 42:52.040
in exchange for my pearls.

42:52.470 --> 42:53.870
Then, what if you lose?

42:54.040 --> 42:55.990
If you lose, you
just give me half the food.

42:59.510 --> 43:01.040
Who said I would give
you groceries?

43:21.155 --> 43:25.425
♪If you forget the fire of love
you once had♪

43:26.665 --> 43:31.845
♪Memories will be destroyed and drowned♪

43:34.595 --> 43:38.735
♪Your heart is full of color♪

43:39.955 --> 43:46.075
♪Makes it hard for me to forget
our relationship♪

43:47.915 --> 43:52.445
♪If longing
is never left behind♪

43:53.245 --> 43:59.275
♪Hoping to return
to the first time we met♪

44:00.175 --> 44:09.465
♪The destined warmth
I want to leave you♪

44:09.635 --> 44:15.845
♪If love can remember
we once promised♪

44:16.195 --> 44:22.105
♪Even though this love hurts me,
I will still live for you♪

44:22.895 --> 44:34.695
♪Pulling out the limits of memory,
waiting is the hardness of my heart♪

44:36.215 --> 44:42.415
♪If love can remember our promise♪

44:42.755 --> 44:49.355
♪Reverse karma,
don't regret ever loving you♪

44:50.665 --> 44:59.595
♪I'm willing to give you my heart
and wait for your answer♪

44:59.595 --> 45:05.715
♪If love can remember our promise♪

45:06.185 --> 45:12.325
♪Reverse karma,
don't regret ever loving you♪

45:14.085 --> 45:25.095
♪I'm willing to give you my heart
and wait for your answer♪

